<st-panel>
  <seckill-form
    isEdit
    v-model="formValue"
    :formCheck="formCheck"
    :form="form"
    :isSubmit="isSubmit"
    @change="onChange"
    @submit="onSubmit"
  >
    <st-form-item labelFix>
      <st-button
        type="primary"
        :loading="loading.editSeckill || formCheck.loading"
        @click="onSave"
      >
        保存
      </st-button>
    </st-form-item>
  </seckill-form>
</st-panel>
